	"notes": "There will be a library of sound effects we will choose from. -JEB 8/31/16\nIncrement TimewsThroughCaptureHJ when reaching here.\nTimewsThroughCaptureHJ should be reset to 0 after OOBE so new enrollees get first-time experience.",
